	<p>Our curriculums integrate low-cost and easy-to-learn hardware such as the Raspberry Pi&trade; with software applications to break down complex subjects into simple pieces and encourage creativity through project-based learning. CurricuPi aims to tackle the gap in STEM education around computer science and prepare youth for the changing workforce. To achieve this, we seek to improve accessibility to high-impact technology courses so that anybody can develop skills in problem-solving, critical thinking, and reasoning through hands-on programming activities and tinkering. 
